<P>THE FEDERALIST: CONTAINING SOME STRICTURES UPON A PAMPHLET, ENTITLED,
<Q><HI>The Preten&s;ions of THOMAS JEFFERSON to the Pre&s;i|dency, examined, and the Charges again&s;t JOHN ADAMS, refuted.</HI></Q></P>
