<P><HI>PHILADELPHIA:</HI> RE-PUBLISHED FROM THE GAZETTE OF <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> AND THE NEW <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> <HI>BY MATHEW CAREY,</HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"></P>
